# Young bilingual students' use of metacognitive strategies to overcome ...

**Source:** https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/full/10.1111/lit.12383
**Crawled:** 2026-06-17

Abstract This study investigates the use of metacognitive strategies by young emergent multilingualstudentsin a translanguaging pedagogy scenario. From a multilingual perspective, we understandmetacognitionas a broader concept that refers to the learning or thinking processes that encapsulate metalinguistic and crosslinguistic awareness.